<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title%></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@3.5.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.css">
  <style>
    *{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    html,body{
      height: 200vh;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #000;
      font-family:"Montserrat" ;
      padding: 16px 14px 0 14px;

    }
    .nav1{
      border-radius: 20px;
      background-color: #dee7e0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 10vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 2%;

    }
    
    nav ul{
      display: flex;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .nav1 ul li{
      margin: 0 8%;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .nav1 ul li a {
        font-size: 2.5vh;
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
        text-wrap: nowrap;
    }
    #Signin-btn{
      font-size: 20px;
      padding: 10px 30px;
      background-color: #434343;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: none;
    }
    .nav2{
      /* border-radius: 20px; */
      background-color: #dee7e0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 6vh;
      display: flex;
      border-left: none;
    }
    .left-border{
      height: 100%;
      width: 8%;
      background-color: #000;
      border-radius: 0  20px 20px 0;
      border: none;
      margin: none;
    }
    
    .center-artical-nav{
      height: 100%;
      width: 84%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center ;
      padding: 0 4%;
      /* overflow: hidden; */
      overflow-x: scroll;
      border: none;
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .center-artical-nav::-webkit-scrollbar {
       display: none;
    }
    .liner-gradint{
      height: 100%;
      width: 4%;
      /* background: linear-gradient(to right,rgb(222,231,),rgb(238, 240, 238),rgb(247, 247, 247)); */
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
    }
    .center-artical-nav ul{
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .center-artical-nav ul li{
      margin: 0 6% 0 0;
      height: 100%;
      /* width: 200px; */
      background-color: #000;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 0 15px;
      
    }
    
    .center-artical-nav ul li a{
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;

    }
    
    .right-border{
      height: 100%;
      width: 8%;
      background-color: #000;
      border: none;
      border-radius:  20px 0 0 20px;
    }
    .main{
      height: 90%;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #000;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .main-info-Con {
      height: 77vh;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background-color: #dee7e0;
      /* background-color: #eae9e8; */
      display: flex;
    }
    .left-main-info-con{
      height: 100%;
      width: 50%;
      /* background-color: gray; */
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4% 2%;
    } 
    .left-main-info-con h1{
      font-size: 70px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .left-main-info-con h2{
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .left-main-info-con p{
      margin: auto;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      line-height: 20px;
      color: #434343;
      width: 70%;
    }
    .right-info-con{
      height: 100%;
      width: 50%;
      /* background-color: blue; */
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .right-info-con img{
      height: 100%;
    }
    .render-articles{
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1% ;
      display: flex;
    }
    .most-views{
      /* height: 100%; */
      width: 34%;
      border: 2px solid #dee7e0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow-y: scroll;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 auto;
      
    }
    .most-views::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }
    .most-views p{
      font-size: 10px;
    }
    .most-views h4{
      color: #fff;
      margin: 1.5% 0;
      font-size: 4vh;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .toparticle{
      height: 200px;
      width: 80%;
      background-color: #dee7e0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      color:#000 ;
      margin-bottom: 2%;
      padding: 1% 2%;
    }
    
    .top-title{
      margin-top: 5px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 83px;
      overflow-y: scroll;
    }
    .top-title::-webkit-scrollbar {
       display: none;
    }
    .toparticle a{
      color: #000;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .rendam-articles{
      height: 100%;
      width: 60%;
      border: 2px solid #dee7e0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-left: 3%;
      /* display: flex; */
      /* justify-content: center; */
      /* align-items: center; */
      flex-direction: column;
      overflow-y: scroll;
      /* padding-top: 2%; */
    }
    .rendam-articles::-webkit-scrollbar {
       display: none;
    }
    .article{
        background-color: #dee7e0;
        height: 20%;
        width: 80%;
        border-radius: 20px;
        display: flex;
        margin: 2% auto;
    }
    .img-con{
        height: 100%;
        width: 30%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        /* justify-content: center; */
        padding-left: 3%;
    }
    .img-con img{
        height: 75%;
        width: 70%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 20px;
        /* margin-right:  */
    }
    .info{
        color: #000;
        padding: 10px 10px;
        /* background-color: green; */
        height: 100%;
        width: 70%;
        border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .info p{
        font-size: 10px;
        color: #000;
        text-align: end;   
    }
    .title-con{
        height: 60%;
        width: 100%;
        /* background-color: red; */
        overflow-y: scroll;
    }
    .title-con::-webkit-scrollbar {
       display: none;
    }
    .action-btns{
        height: 20%;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
    }

    /* 
  ##Device = Desktops
  ##Screen = 1281px to higher resolution desktops
*/

@media (min-width: 1281px) {
  
  
  
}

/* 
  ##Device = Laptops, Desktops
  ##Screen = B/w 1025px to 1280px
*/

@media (min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 1280px) {
  
  .article{
    width: 90%;
  }
  .toparticle{
    width: 90%;
  }
  .top-title h2{
    font-size: 2.5vh;
  }
  .title-con h2{
    font-size: 2.5vh;
  }
}

/* 
  ##Device = Tablets, Ipads (portrait)
  ##Screen = B/w 768px to 1024px
*/

@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
  
  .right-info-con img{
    height: 80%;
  }
  .left-main-info-con h1{
      font-size: 4vw;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      margin-top: 70px;
  }
  .left-main-info-con h2{
    font-size: 2vw;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .toparticle{
    width: 95%;
    height: 18%;
  }
  .top-title h2{
    font-size: 2vw;
  }
  .article{
    width: 95%;
    height: 15%;
  }
  .article a{
    font-size: 12px;
  }
  .title-con h2{
    font-size: 2vw;
  }
  
}

/* 
  ##Device = Tablets, Ipads (landscape)
  ##Screen = B/w 768px to 1024px
*/

@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) and (orientation: landscape) {
  

  
}

/* 
  ##Device = Low Resolution Tablets, Mobiles (Landscape)
  ##Screen = B/w 481px to 767px
*/

@media (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 767px) {
  
  .nav1 ul li{
    margin: 0 2%;
      
  }
  .nav1 ul li a{
    font-size: 1.8vh;
    
  }
  .logo{
    padding-right: 20vw;
  }
.main-info-Con {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.left-main-info-con{
  width: 100%;
  /* background-color: red; */
  text-align: center;
  /* padding: 4% 2%; */
} 
.left-main-info-con h1{
  font-size: 10vw;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.left-main-info-con h2{
  font-size: 5vw;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.right-info-con{
  width: 100%;
  /* background-color: blue; */
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}
.right-info-con img{
  height: 50vh;
  margin-right: 30px;
}
  
}

/* 
  ##Device = Most of the Smartphones Mobiles (Portrait)
  ##Screen = B/w 320px to 479px
*/

@media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 650px) {
  .logo{
    padding-right: 15vw;
  }
  #Signin-btn{
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 6px 15px;
      background-color: #434343;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: none;
  }
  .render-articles{
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 200vh;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .most-views{
    height: 100vh;
    width: 80vw;
  }
  .rendam-articles{
    width: 90vw;
    height: 100vh;
    margin-top: 10px;
    /* padding: 1% 1%; */
  }
  .article{
    width: 90%;
    height: 15%;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }
}
@media (min-width: 320px) and (max-width: 480px) {
  
  /* CSS */
  
}

    
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav1 ">
    <ul class="d-flex ">
      <li class="logo"><a href="">News Hub</a></li>
      <li ><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li ><a href="/About">About</a></li>
      <li ><a href="/Contacts">Contacts</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="btn btn-dark fs-5" id="Signin-btn" onclick="redirectToSingIn()" >Sing in</button>
  </nav>
  <nav class="nav2">
    <div class="left-border">
    </div>
    <div class="center-artical-nav">
      <ul>
        <!-- <div class="liner-gradint"></div> -->
        <li><a href="/articles/Politics">Politics</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Business">Business</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Technology">Technology</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Science">Science</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Health">Health</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Sports">Sports</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Entertainment">Entertainment</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Environment">Environment</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Lifestyl">Lifestyl</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles/Education">Education</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="blank"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="right-border"></div>
  </nav>
  <div class="main">
    <div class="main-info-Con">
      <div class="left-main-info-con">
          <h1>News Hub</h1>
          <h2>Where Knowledge Meets Discovery</h2>
          <p>Welcome to News Hub Hero, your trusted destination for breaking news from around the globe. We are your front-row seat to the most compelling stories, providing you with up-to-the-minute updates on politics, business, technology, entertainment, and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="right-info-con">
        <img src="/images/[removal.ai]_tmp-6494d05c3ab39.png" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="render-articles">
      <div class="most-views">
        <h4>Top</h4>
        <% toparticles.forEach(function(article,index) { %>
          <div class="toparticle">
            <p><%= article.createdAt.toLocaleDateString('en-IN', {
              day: '2-digit',
              month: '2-digit',
              year: 'numeric',
            })%></p>
            <div class="top-title">

              <h2><%= article.Title %></h2>
            </div>
            <a href="/article/<%= article.id%>">read more</a>
          </div>
        <% }); %>

      </div>
      <div class="rendam-articles">
        <% articles.forEach(function(article,index) { %>
          <div class="article">
              <div class="img-con">
                  <img src="/images/articleimages/<%= article.Image %>" alt="">
              </div>
              <div class="info">
                  <p><%= article.createdAt.toLocaleDateString('en-IN', {
                    day: '2-digit',
                    month: '2-digit',
                    year: 'numeric',
                  })%></p>
                  <div class="title-con">
                      <h2><%= article.Title %></h2>
                  </div>
                  <div class="action-btns">
                      <p><%= article.Category%></p>
                      <a href="/article/<%= article.id%>">read more</a>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src=""></script>
  <script>
    function redirectToSingIn() {
      window.location.href = '/Signin';
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>